{"id":"the-shy-turtle","slug":"the-shy-turtle","title":"The Shy Turtle","title_ko":"부끄럼쟁이 거북이","level":"A1","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/cover.webp","summary_ko":"부끄러워 등딱지에 숨던 거북이가 용기를 내어 첫 친구를 사귀는 하루예요.","wordCount":98,"pages":[{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Tilly was a small green turtle.","translation_ko":"틸리는 작은 초록 거북이였어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Tilly","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"was","charStart":6,"charEnd":9,"startMs":360,"endMs":740},{"word":"a","charStart":10,"charEnd":11,"startMs":740,"endMs":1040},{"word":"small","charStart":12,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1320},{"word":"green","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1700},{"word":"turtle","charStart":24,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1700,"endMs":1960}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"She was very shy.","translation_ko":"틸리는 무척 부끄럼이 많았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"was","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":260,"endMs":480},{"word":"very","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":480,"endMs":840},{"word":"shy","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":840,"endMs":1100}]}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"When other animals came near, she hid.","translation_ko":"다른 동물들이 가까이 오면, 틸리는 숨었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"When","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"other","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":240,"endMs":620},{"word":"animals","charStart":11,"charEnd":18,"startMs":620,"endMs":960},{"word":"came","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":960,"endMs":1320},{"word":"near","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1580},{"word":"she","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2240},{"word":"hid","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2480}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"She pulled her head into her shell.","translation_ko":"머리를 등딱지 속으로 쏙 집어넣었지요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":740},{"word":"pulled","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":740,"endMs":1040},{"word":"her","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1240},{"word":"head","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1520},{"word":"into","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1980},{"word":"her","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2260},{"word":"shell","charStart":29,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2440}]}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"One day a frog hopped to the pond.","translation_ko":"어느 날 개구리 한 마리가 연못으로 폴짝 뛰어왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"day","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":380,"endMs":740},{"word":"a","charStart":8,"charEnd":9,"startMs":880,"endMs":1500},{"word":"frog","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1500},{"word":"hopped","charStart":15,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1920},{"word":"to","charStart":22,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2160},{"word":"the","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2600},{"word":"pond","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2600,"endMs":2620}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Hi! I am Fred,\" he said.","translation_ko":"\"안녕! 난 프레드야,\" 개구리가 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Hi","charStart":1,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"I","charStart":5,"charEnd":6,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1340},{"word":"am","charStart":7,"charEnd":9,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1560},{"word":"Fred","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1880},{"word":"he","charStart":17,"charEnd":19,"startMs":2620,"endMs":2760},{"word":"said","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":2760,"endMs":3020}]}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"Tilly hid in her shell again.","translation_ko":"틸리는 다시 등딱지 속에 숨었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Tilly","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"hid","charStart":6,"charEnd":9,"startMs":400,"endMs":720},{"word":"in","charStart":10,"charEnd":12,"startMs":720,"endMs":880},{"word":"her","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":880,"endMs":1080},{"word":"shell","charStart":17,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1300},{"word":"again","charStart":23,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1640}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"But Fred sat down and waited.","translation_ko":"하지만 프레드는 자리에 앉아 기다려 주었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"Fred","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":380,"endMs":680},{"word":"sat","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":680,"endMs":980},{"word":"down","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":980,"endMs":1340},{"word":"and","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1580},{"word":"waited","charStart":22,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1780}]}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"Slowly, Tilly peeked out.","translation_ko":"천천히, 틸리가 살며시 고개를 내밀었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Slowly","charStart":0,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":740},{"word":"Tilly","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1400},{"word":"peeked","charStart":14,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1900},{"word":"out","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2040}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"Fred gave her a warm smile.","translation_ko":"프레드가 따뜻하게 웃어 주었지요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Fred","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"gave","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":380,"endMs":780},{"word":"her","charStart":10,"charEnd":13,"startMs":780,"endMs":920},{"word":"a","charStart":14,"charEnd":15,"startMs":920,"endMs":1300},{"word":"warm","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1560},{"word":"smile","charStart":21,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1980}]}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"Do you want to play?\" Fred asked.","translation_ko":"\"같이 놀래?\" 프레드가 물었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Do","charStart":1,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":520},{"word":"you","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":520,"endMs":740},{"word":"want","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":740,"endMs":880},{"word":"to","charStart":13,"charEnd":15,"startMs":880,"endMs":1320},{"word":"play","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1320},{"word":"Fred","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2080},{"word":"asked","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2500}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"Tilly nodded and stepped out.","translation_ko":"틸리는 고개를 끄덕이며 밖으로 나왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Tilly","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"nodded","charStart":6,"charEnd":12,"startMs":380,"endMs":1060},{"word":"and","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1540},{"word":"stepped","charStart":17,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1680},{"word":"out","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1680,"endMs":2000}]}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"They swam and splashed all day.","translation_ko":"둘은 하루 종일 헤엄치고 물장구를 쳤어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"swam","charStart":5,"charEnd":9,"startMs":320,"endMs":800},{"word":"and","charStart":10,"charEnd":13,"startMs":800,"endMs":1180},{"word":"splashed","charStart":14,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1520},{"word":"all","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1920},{"word":"day","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2240}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"Tilly laughed for the first time.","translation_ko":"틸리는 난생처음 깔깔 웃었답니다.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Tilly","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"laughed","charStart":6,"charEnd":13,"startMs":460,"endMs":1040},{"word":"for","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1500},{"word":"the","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1680},{"word":"first","charStart":22,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1680,"endMs":1860},{"word":"time","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2160}]}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"Now Tilly was not shy with Fred.","translation_ko":"이제 틸리는 프레드와 함께라면 부끄럽지 않았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Now","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":660},{"word":"Tilly","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":660,"endMs":1320},{"word":"was","charStart":10,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1760},{"word":"not","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2200},{"word":"shy","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2440},{"word":"with","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2820},{"word":"Fred","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2820,"endMs":3080}]},{"id":"the-shy-turtle-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"She had a friend, and she smiled.","translation_ko":"친구가 생긴 틸리는 환하게 미소 지었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-shy-turtle/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"had","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":280,"endMs":400},{"word":"a","charStart":8,"charEnd":9,"startMs":400,"endMs":580},{"word":"friend","charStart":10,"charEnd":16,"startMs":580,"endMs":820},{"word":"and","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1360},{"word":"she","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1540},{"word":"smiled","charStart":26,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1800}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"틸리는 어떤 동물인가요?","type":"mc","options":["작은 초록 거북이","큰 노란 개구리","갈색 토끼","하얀 오리"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"틸리는 작은 초록 거북이예요.","id":"the-shy-turtle-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"다른 동물이 가까이 오면 틸리는 무엇을 했나요?","type":"mc","options":["크게 인사했어요","등딱지 속에 숨었어요","도망쳤어요","노래를 불렀어요"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"틸리는 부끄러워서 머리를 등딱지 속으로 집어넣고 숨었어요.","id":"the-shy-turtle-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"연못으로 찾아온 친구의 이름은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["톰","프레드","샘","맥스"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"연못으로 뛰어온 개구리의 이름은 프레드예요.","id":"the-shy-turtle-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"프레드는 숨은 틸리에게 어떻게 했나요?","type":"mc","options":["화를 냈어요","그냥 가버렸어요","앉아서 기다려 주었어요","큰 소리로 불렀어요"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"프레드는 틸리를 재촉하지 않고 조용히 앉아 기다려 주었어요.","id":"the-shy-turtle-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 우리에게 주는 마음은 무엇일까요?","type":"mc","options":["용기를 내면 친구를 사귈 수 있어요","숨는 것이 가장 안전해요","혼자 노는 게 제일 좋아요","빨리 헤엄쳐야 이겨요"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"부끄러워도 조금 용기를 내면 좋은 친구를 만날 수 있다는 따뜻한 이야기예요.","id":"the-shy-turtle-q5","ord":4}]}